text: Update: 3,591 new #COVID19 cases and 42 deaths reported today. Take action and always wear a mask in public even if you do not feel sick. Maintain physical distancing. Stay home when sick. We must work together to slow the spread of COVID-19 #MaskUpAZ https://t.co/iI5Co8uw9c
